FROM hf.co/mradermacher/gemma-4-26B-A4B-it-ultra-uncensored-heretic-i1-GGUF:i1-Q5_K_M
# mradermacher imatrix (i1) Q5_K_M requant of llmfan46's "ultra-uncensored-heretic"
# (Heretic 1.2.0 + ARA on attn.o_proj L11-22; reported 3/100 refusals, KL 0.1237,
# MMLU 79.99 vs 82.48 base). Gemma-4-26B-A4B MoE: 25.2B total / ~3.8B active -> fast
# when offloaded into RAM. i1-Q5_K_M chosen over Q6_K for a higher GPU-resident
# fraction on 12 GB VRAM at negligible quality cost (imatrix narrows the Q5<->Q6 gap).
# Ollama's built-in gemma4 RENDERER handles the chat template (Claude-Code-safe);
# confirm with the 3-system-message smoke test before trusting.

# --- CONTEXT CALIBRATION (26B-A4B max is 262144) ---
PARAMETER num_ctx 200000
PARAMETER num_predict 65536

# --- GOOGLE/UNSLOTH RECOMMENDED GEMMA 4 PARAMETERS ---
# Verified against unsloth.ai/docs/models/gemma-4: temp 1.0, top_p 0.95, top_k 64.
PARAMETER temperature 1.0
PARAMETER top_p 0.95
PARAMETER top_k 64

# Neutral; Gemma 4 needs no repeat penalty (not specified upstream).
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.0

# Gemma 4 thinking: activate with <|think|> at the start of the system prompt.
SYSTEM <|think|>
